# Folder Usage

- `src/components`: reusable, presentation-focused UI blocks used by multiple screens.
- `src/screens`: route-level screens and screen composition.
- `src/navigation`: route names, navigator setup, and navigation helpers.
- `src/context`: React context providers, reducers/state, and exposed hooks.
- `src/services`: storage adapters, API clients, and side-effectful business operations.
- `src/types`: shared app/domain types and interfaces.
- `src/utils`: pure helper functions with no side effects.

If code does not clearly belong to one folder, default to the layer that reduces coupling.
